                <div class="summary">
                    <p> For a more complete list of publications, including all collaborative manuscripts,  please refer to my <a href="Guindani_curriculum.pdf"> Curriculum Vitae (CV).</a> <br/>
                    Links to my professional pages on   <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/michele-guindani-8a05872" target="_blank"> LinkedIn </a> ,  <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Michele_Guindani2" target="_blank"> Research Gate </a>,  <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=1c0SrIoAAAAJ&hl=en" target="_blank"> Google Scholar </a>,  <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=Guindani%2C+Michele%5BAuthor%5D" target="_blank"> PubMed </a> and <a href="http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6363-9907" target="_blank"> Orcid </a> can be found on the sidebar on the left. 
