Hanasono M and Fingeret MC (2016). 
<a href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/hed.24415/abstract">
Salient Body Image and Psychosocial
Concerns of Cancer Patients Undergoing Head and Neck Reconstruction.</a>
<i>Head and Neck</i>, <b>38(7)</b>, 1035-1042.
</p>



<p>
