Antzack P, Clarke K, Davies N, Rahman A, Campbell M, Guindani M,
Bicknell R, Vannucci M. and Falciani F (2016).
<a href="papers/Trevino_Cassese_PLoSCompBio.pdf">
A Network Biology Approach Identifies Molecular Cross-talk between Normal 
Prostate Epithelial and Prostate Carcinoma Cells.</a>
<i>PLoS Computational Biology</i>, <b>12(4)</b>, e1004884. (PMCID:
PMC4849722)
</p>


<p>
