<i>Biometrics</i>, <b>71</b>, 803-811. 
<i> Biometrics </i>, <b>71 (1) </b>, 188-97. See also the <a href="papers/Cassese_Daphnia_Magna_biom-supp.pdf"> supplementary material. </a>  (PMID: 25771699, PMCID: PMC4880373)
</p>




<p>
<b>[14]</b> Graziani R, Guindani M, Thall PF (2015)
<a href="papers/Graziani_et_al-2015-Biometrics.pdf"> Bayesian nonparametric
estimation of targeted agent effects on biomarker change to predict
clinical outcome </a>
<i> Biometrics </i>, <b>71 (1) </b>, 188-97. See also the <a href="papers/Graziani_Biom_2015-supp.pdf"> supplementary material. </a> (PMCID: PMC4383707) 
</p>




<p>
<b>[13]</b> Sun W, Reich B, Cai T, Guindani M, Schwartzman A (2015)
